page_title: 'Use the Azure Developer CLI to deploy resources for Azure OpenAI On Your Data'
page_description: Use this article to learn how to automate resource deployment for Azure OpenAI On Your Data.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- Access granted to Azure OpenAI in the desired Azure subscription. Azure OpenAI requires registration and is currently only available to approved enterprise customers and partners. See Limited access to Azure OpenAI Service for more information. You can apply for access to Azure OpenAI by completing the form at https://aka.ms/oai/access. Open an issue on this repo to contact us if you have an issue.- The Azure Developer CLI installed on your machine
